_sText:
This is my very first map, Very popular on some servers for some odd reason, This was made way before I knew about scaling so if you jump you WILL hit your head on something other wise a good cramped-type map.

There's only 1 bombsite as well, And it's at the top.

Created: I forget when cos there have been various versions, With updates to lighting and maps.
This one is the Wednesday, 22 February 2006 version anyway.
